CatDescriptText: Rosedale gas station at Tioga Street was also used as a jitney cab station.  It is a small building with tile roof and two gas pumps out front.  The three story apartment buildings across the street have been replaced with new Ryan Homes.  In the background cars are waiting to be repaired and a young girl puts air in her bicycle tires.  Sunflowers grow on the right.
TitMainTitle: Mobil gas station across street from Brushton Food Co. Wholesale Grocers, Rosedale and Tioga Streets, Homewood
